(127, 6, 'mfn-page-items-seo', '<br /><h1 style=\"padding:40px 0px 10px 40px; font-size:300%; color:#596d6a;\"><b>About Us</b></h1>\r\n<p class=\"big\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 60px; font-size:120%; color:#596d6a;\">We at Neon Consultancy are not only concerned with the quality of services but also care for our approach, value, commitment and behaviors towards fulfillment of client\'s objective. With a strong belief in individuality of each client, we always endeavor to provide personalized professional services with commitment to each client while adhering to the best of professional norms and practices with utmost dynamism.</p>\r\n<p class=\"big\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 60px; font-size:120%; color:#596d6a;\">With the current Global competitiveness and era of Corporate Governance in the background of information hungry society, every move by any corporate, commercial establishments or individual needs specialized guidance by professionals having expertise in the relevant field. The team of Legal Professionals supported with adequate number of Research Associates at Neon Consultancy ensures that our clients is equipped with the most updated requirements and prepared to remain always A Leader.</p>\n\njustify\n\nhttp://neonmitesh.com/resource/Image/home.jpg\n\n150\n\n<h1  class=\"m\" style=\"padding: 40px 0px 10px 40px; font-size:300%; color:#596d6a;\"><b>About Mitesh Shah</b></h1>\r\n<p class=\"big\" style=\"padding:10px 0px 0px 60px; font-size:200%; color:#4d5a87;\"><u><i>Education:</i></u></p>\r\n<ul style=\"color:#596d6a; padding:0px 0px 0px 80px;\">\r\n<li>B Com.</li>\r\n<li>S T P (Sales Tax Practitioner)</li>\r\n<li>I T P (Income Tax Practitioner)</li>\r\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"big\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 60px; font-size:200%; color:#4d5a87;\"><u><i>Nature of Practise:</i></u></p>\r\n<div class=\"column one-third\">\r\n<ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px;color:#596d6a;\">\r\n<li>Tax Consultant Practice In </li>\r\n<li>Assessment In Vat Tax</li>\r\n<li>Assessment In Income Tax</li>\r\n<li>Assessment In Professional Tax</li>\r\n<li>Sales Tax, Income Tax, G S T , Professional Tax</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"column one-third\"><ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px;color:#596d6a;\">\r\n<li>In Future Assessment In G S T</li>\r\n<li>Appeal In Sales Tax</li>\r\n<li>Appeal In Income Tax</li>\r\n<li>E Payment for Vat & Income Tax</li>\r\n<li>Professional In Books Of Accounts Writings</li>\r\n</ul></div>\r\n<div class=\"column one-third\"><ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px;color:#596d6a;\">\r\n<li>Filing Of Personnel l Income Tax Returns</li>\r\n<li>Filing Of Service Tax Returns</li>\r\n<li>Filing of Vat Audit & Income Tax Audit</li>\r\n<li>Bank Loans: Housing Loans, Cash Credit Loans</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"big\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 60px; font-size:200%; color:#4d5a87;\"><u><i>Past Experience:</i></u></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px; color:#596d6a; font-size:120%;\">My qualification is B Com done in 1989. Took tax practice, Sales Tax & Income Tax Practice & audit under my uncle<span><b> Mr Arvind K Shah ( C A )</b></span> at Borivali.\r\nFrom 1992, started practice under the name of Ms n e o n Consultancy at Borivali west.</p>\n\n<h1 style=\"padding: 40px 0px 30px 40px; font-size:300%; color:#596d6a;\"><b>Our Team</b></h1>\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px; color:#596d6a; font-size:120%;\">Our dedicated team comprises of competent people with extensive knowledge and experience. Our professionalism and expertise helps us to service our clients to their satisfaction.\r\n</p><br /><br />\r\n<p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px; color:#596d6a; font-size:120%;\">We are Tie-up in with practising with Professional Nos.</p>\n\n<ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px;color:#596d6a;\">\r\n<li>CA Arvind K. Shah</li>\r\n<li>CA Deepak Mehta</li>\r\n<li>CA Usha Mulay</li>\r\n<li>CA  Ajit Shah</li>\r\n</ul>\n\n<ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px;color:#596d6a;\">\r\n<li>CA Nilesh Timabadia</li>\r\n<li>CA HItesh Shah</li>\r\n<li>CA Dharmesh Thar</li>\r\n<li>CS Parag Mulay</li>\r\n</ul>\n\n<ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 70px;color:#596d6a;\">\r\n<li>Tax Practisner - Mahendra Shah</li>\r\n<li>Tax Practisner - Jayant Doshi</li>\r\n<li>Adv. Vijay Rajput</li>\r\n</ul>\n\n<table><thead style=\"font-size:120%; background-color:#3f3d3d !important;\">\r\n<tr><th>Sr no.</th>\r\n<th>Name of staff</th>\r\n<th>Qualification</th>\r\n<th>Contact No.</th>\r\n<th>Designation</th>\r\n</tr></thead><tbody style=\"font-size:120%;\"><tr>\r\n<td>1</td>\r\n<td>Aarti Kore</td>\r\n<td>(B Com)</td>\r\n<td>9222257922</td>\r\n<td>UpLoad in Vat & Income Tax Returns & Audit Report</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr><td>2</td>\r\n<td>Sneha Darji</td>\r\n<td>(B Com)</td>\r\n<td>9222257922</td>\r\n<td>Up Load in Vat & Income Tax returns</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr><td>3</td>\r\n<td>Mamta Salvi</td>\r\n<td>(B Com)</td>\r\n<td>7021349001</td>\r\n<td>For G S T Registration & Books Of Accounts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr><td>4</td>\r\n<td>Mahima Waghela</td>\r\n<td>(B Com)</td>\r\n<td>9222258922</td>\r\n<td>Books Of Accounts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n\r\n<tr><td>5</td>\r\n<td>Pradeep Sawant</td>\r\n<td>(B Com)</td>\r\n<td>7977982040</td>\r\n<td>Dispatch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\n\nfadeInLeft\n\n'),
